---
source: src/cli/mod.rs
assertion: review workspace scopes evidence to workspace path with determinism
schema:
  response: ee.response.v1
  review: ee.review.workspace.v1
contracts:
  - workspace scope filters evidence to path or current directory
  - include-cass flag controls CASS-derived evidence inclusion
  - propose flag generates curation candidates from workspace evidence
  - dry-run preview without writing candidate records
  - JSON stdout is ee.response.v1 envelope
  - degrades honestly when CASS evidence unavailable
evidence:
  - ReviewWorkspaceArgs.scope
  - ReviewWorkspaceArgs.include_cass
  - ReviewWorkspaceArgs.propose
  - ReviewWorkspaceArgs.dry_run
  - ReviewWorkspaceReport.schema
  - ReviewWorkspaceReport.memory_count
  - ReviewWorkspaceReport.evidence_count
  - ReviewWorkspaceReport.candidates
